勾勒出 scientific explanations 嘅結構。"},{"pid":"111b6db172ff43905bd40f5ad8757c30fd371c9f","tid":1888377,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8482268e972dca0770d3960178d1024e75edb67b","tid":1888377,"uid":126973,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"完全錯漏百出<br />\n<br />\n科學哲學唔係基本邏輯，兩者都唔係圍繞住實證論和懷疑論<br />\n一般入門嘅科學哲學會讀 Karl Popper嘅證偽主義，<br />\nHempel 講 confirmation<br />\nThomas Kuhn 講「科學範式」，「科學革命」<br />\n但基本邏輯根本唔會讀呢啲野<br />\n<br />\n陳雲呢篇文講嘅 models of explanation，已經見到佢唔識咩叫 models of explanation<br />\n科學家會用 models 解釋現象，但呢啲用 models 嘅解釋，應該叫 model explanations，或者叫 model-based explanations。<br />\n<br />\nModels of explanation 就係另一回事，字面意思係，explanation 嘅 models。即係咩意思？科學哲學會探討點先構成一個 scientific explanation，哲學家會提出唔同 models 去勾勒出 scientific explanations 嘅結構。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"非台巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />久仰大名"},{"pid":"43a9081f0e28b4ca860e3b92e8d56d4b91b01f7b","tid":1888377,"uid":265192,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"佢得閒撻兩個學術詞彙出黎<br />\n呃鳩班讀書少既青城傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾年成班熱狗學人講「新自由主義」<br />\n開口埋口都提住，笑撚死我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1ca105fa2277db5cc8c854c2bb52f7be9e1f3c","tid":1888377,"uid":166236,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3e8ac6cda0162909c906d2015eca0648cd3a8094","tid":1888377,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"在二次大戰之後，物理學界出現量子力學的突破，調整傳統的牛頓力學，而且蘇聯提供了另外的科學研究，於是科學哲學就有很大的進步，成為哲學的一門。<br />\n<br />\n好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心唔好衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"科學哲學是20世紀興起的一個哲學分支<br />\nby wiki<br />\n<br />\n老尷d乜？"},{"pid":"18d3877bbe7e1481eb2