b91b01f7b","tid":1888377,"uid":265192,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"佢得閒撻兩個學術詞彙出黎<br />\n呃鳩班讀書少既青城傻仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾年成班熱狗學人講「新自由主義」<br />\n開口埋口都提住，笑撚死我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"咁先仆街，陳雲嗰種識少少似是而非扮到好撚高深咁，慢慢培育咗嗰班信徒好難甩，好彩嘅係得嗰千幾個，但佢真係好撚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4760320ba743f19cab67db433082e24dca6e59a8","tid":1888377,"uid":126973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da1ca105fa2277db5cc8c854c2bb52f7be9e1f3c","tid":1888377,"uid":166236,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3e8ac6cda0162909c906d2015eca0648cd3a8094","tid":1888377,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"在二次大戰之後，物理學界出現量子力學的突破，調整傳統的牛頓力學，而且蘇聯提供了另外的科學研究，於是科學哲學就有很大的進步，成為哲學的一門。<br />\n<br />\n好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心唔好衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:43:53.000Z","msg":"科學哲學是20世紀興起的一個哲學分支<br />\nby wiki<br />\n<br />\n老尷d乜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"1） 二戰之前已經有量子力學，主要係 1920-1930年發展出黎 <br />\n2）一般會話，相對論取代咗牛頓力學<br />\n3） 將科學哲學嘅興起 睇成係因為有量子力學 同乜乜 蘇聯科學研究  <br />\n似乎十分誤導 <br />\n<br />\n反而 係科學哲學對量子力學，相對論嘅發展 有一定影響<br />\nCarlo Rovelli呢個物理學家指出：<br />\n<br />\nBoth major advances made by twentieth century physics were strongly influenced by philosophy... Quantum mechanics springs from an intuition due to Heisenberg, grounded in the strongly positivist philosophical atmosphere in which he found himself: one gets knowledge by restricting oneself to what is observable. The abstract of Heisenberg&rsquo;s 1925 milestone paper on quantum theory is explicit about this: <br />\n<br />\nThe aim of this work is to set the basis for a theory of quantum mechanics based exclusively on relations between quantities that are in principle observable [7]. <br />\n<br />\nThe same distinctly philosophical attitude nourished Einstein&rsquo;s discovery of special relativity: by restricting to what is observable, we recognise that the notion of simultaneity is misleading. Einstein explicitly recognised his debt to the philosophical writings of Mach and Poincar&eacute;."},{"pid":"1bb4f582b4e421c3b0791c21be4ff2852dad2583","tid":1888377,"uid":19487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"佢直頭係痴線<br />\n唔係唔識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548a03eb37ba1c352cda09b62c33db0766642ea8","tid":1888377,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:30:51.000Z","msg":"單單講&quot;量子力學調整牛頓力學&quot;又唔可以話錯晒既，雖然一般呢句話會用喺相對論嗰到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132f36c1e485ba192f2925978cc587763534b81f","tid":1888377,"uid":245484,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"條友識既野樣樣都好撚表面 <br />\n資料又唔準確 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係得D 冇乜點讀過書又蠢既人先會當佢神咁拜"},{"pid":"af2d2b8b4bb17a89fe63fe4ef3757f5b8960aade","tid":1888377,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"18d3877bbe7e1481eb280f13054ef681cfc4f323","tid":1888377,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1ca105fa2277db5cc8c854c2bb52f7be9e1f3c","tid":1888377,"uid":166236,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3e8ac6cda0162909c906d2015eca0648cd3a8094","tid":1888377,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"在二次大戰之後，物理學界出現量子力學的突破，調整傳統的牛頓力學，而且蘇聯提供了另外的科學研究，於是科學哲學就有很大的進步，成為哲學的一門。<br />\n<br />\n好撚老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心唔好衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji